00:06:20.250 --> 00:06:22.000
So what else can we figure out?

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:23.950
So let's see.

00:06:23.950 --> 00:06:25.530
I mean, I don't to be
tacky without any

00:06:25.530 --> 00:06:26.930
