00:06:26.930 --> 00:06:31.550
We have this angle here.

00:06:31.550 --> 00:06:33.470
And what other angles are
equal to this angle?

00:06:33.470 --> 00:06:37.320
Well, we can use our parallel
lines and transversal of

00:06:37.320 --> 00:06:42.350
