whatever, and figure it out.

00:06:42.350 --> 00:06:44.860
Well this angle
corresponds to what?

00:06:44.860 --> 00:06:46.620
Well, it corresponds
to this angle.

00:06:46.620 --> 00:06:48.320
So it's equivalent.

00:06:48.320 --> 00:06:49.750
And you got that from
your parallel lines.

00:06:49.750 --> 00:06:50.090
Right?

00:06:50.090 --> 00:06:52.000
So these two are the same.

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:57.150
And then, finally, if I have--
let me pick a good color-- if I

00:06:57.150 --> 00:06:59.550
have this angle, draw
a triple angle here.

00:06:59.550 --> 00:07:00.110
Same thing.

00:07:00.110 --> 00:07:02.610
This corresponding angle is
going to be right here.

00:07:05.250 --> 00:07:05.830
So there.

